Output demo/nix-search-demo.gif
Set Theme "Aardvark Blue"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 700
Set Shell "zsh"

Type "cargo run -- claude"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type " co"
Sleep 1800ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Up
Sleep 1100ms
Ctrl+u
Sleep 900ms
Type "pg"
Sleep 1400ms
Backspace
Sleep 800ms
Type "ostgresql"
Sleep 1800ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Up
Sleep 900ms
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
